1
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:40,320
Li Yunxi,

2
00:01:40,759 --> 00:01:41,759
this jade pendant

3
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:43,680
was given to me by Mother.

4
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:44,820
If you put it on,

5
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:47,759
you can never take it off, even in death.

6
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:48,450
Alright.

7
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:50,960
The biggest regret of my life

8
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:52,880
is marrying you

9
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:55,570
and coming to this cage of a palace.

10
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:57,960
If I had a second chance,

11
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,920
I'd rather marry Li Yunmo

12
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:04,680
than marry you.

13
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:07,520
Want to leave my side?

14
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,840
Unless I die.

15
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,360
You want me to stay?

16
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:14,400
Unless I die.

17
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:15,840
Don't go.

18
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:34,880
This is the wolf tooth I hunted myself.

19
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:35,540
It's yours.

20
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:39,840
Ling.

21
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,880
Even if you don't love me,

22
00:02:46,160 --> 00:02:48,280
I won't let you leave me.

23
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:58,760
Since ancient times, the strong have ruled over life and death,

24
00:02:58,760 --> 00:03:01,090
while the lives of the weak are worthless.

25
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,720
Today, I'll show you

26
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:06,370
what it feels like to have your limbs severed.

27
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:09,080
Empress,

28
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,520
you lunatic!

29
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:11,400
Stop!

30
00:03:17,079 --> 00:03:19,120
Your Majesty, save me.

31
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,600
Empress, what are you doing?

32
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,970
Consort Xue, Lady Liu, is so audacious

33
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:28,200
as to put Love Potion in my pastries.

34
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:30,360
I am merely giving her a small punishment.

35
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,160
Your Majesty,

36
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,200
I am innocent.

37
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,560
What Love Potion?

38
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,520
I have never even heard of it,

39
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:37,640
let alone poison the Empress.

40
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:39,570
Hanxing.

41
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,160
Your Majesty.

42
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:44,280
This is the medicine bottle I found in Feixue Palace.

43
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,610
It contains Qingsirao.

44
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,720
Empress, you...

45
00:03:58,079 --> 00:03:59,720
You are just envious that I

46
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,120
possess His Majesty's favor.

47
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,240
Su Kuang,

48
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,380
check what's inside this bottle.

49
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:12,080
Yes.

50
00:04:17,440 --> 00:04:19,240
This isn't Qingsirao at all.

51
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:23,440
It is the Ice Dew I made myself.

52
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,600
Your Majesty,

53
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:31,640
I have been wrongly accused.

54
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:35,720
Please do justice for me.

55
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:02,640
The Empress has killed someone!

56
00:05:08,840 --> 00:05:09,640
Your Majesty,

57
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:12,660
the deceased is Ruyan, a maid from Jile Hall.

58
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:14,480
She has been missing for two days.

59
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,540
The Empress has been looking for her.

60
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:17,700
When she was found,

61
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,960
she had been dead for a long time.

62
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:23,240
Why have I heard rumors about the Empress?

63
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:26,400
A dagger was stuck in the deceased's chest,

64
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:28,240
and she was holding a medicine bottle.

65
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:30,120
After the Imperial Physician's examination,

66
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:32,400
it was said that the bottle once contained Qingsirao.

67
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,280
Rumor has it that

68
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:35,120
the Empress was jealous of Consort Xue's favor,

69
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:37,050
so she used Qingsirao to frame her.

70
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,920
Unexpectedly, the plot was exposed.

71
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,450
In a fit of rage, the Empress

72
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:43,440
killed the witness, Ruyan, to silence her.

73
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:49,080
His Majesty has arrived.

74
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:56,360
What brings Your Majesty here?

75
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:58,420
I heard you are investigating Ruyan.

76
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:05,800
So, Your Majesty has come to interrogate me.

77
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:09,920
What secret is Ruyan hiding?

78
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:12,360
You've been acting strange lately.

79
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,960
You're not usually so aggressive.

80
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:15,160
Then, Your Majesty,

81
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,480
do you believe I am innocent?

82
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:18,800
I mean,

83
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:21,200
everything requires evidence.

84
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:24,100
Does evidence really matter?

85
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:33,980
What are you doing?

86
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,340
You trust Consort Xue so much.

87
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:39,640
Is it because

88
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:41,680
she knows how to pretend to be gentle

89
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,600
and pitiful?

90
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,000
You are my woman.

91
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:57,200
I won't let Li Yunmo have you.

92
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,280
Yunmo.

93
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:04,530
Calling his name late at night,

94
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,800
and so intimately too.

95
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:08,760
I...

96
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:13,600
Get out.

97
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:17,680
You're crazy.

98
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:20,360
You were the one who brought up Li Yunmo.

99
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,420
Fine, I'm leaving.

100
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:22,940
Your Highness.

101
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,320
Wait.

102
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:26,960
You should be the one leaving.

103
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:28,090
This is my Jile Hall.

104
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,760
Return to the palace.

105
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,600
Lunatic.

106
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,500
Greetings, Your Majesty.

107
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:14,800
I said I could show you favor,

108
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:18,280
but you must not cause trouble at the Hall of Bliss.

109
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:23,810
You rarely visit me, Your Majesty.

110
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:26,680
Did you come just to scold me?

111
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:29,960
I am just a weak woman.

112
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:33,640
How could I take a life?

113
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:38,520
Liu Mianmian.

114
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:42,720
Just because I don't expose you doesn't mean I don't know.

115
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:45,450
You'd better not forget why I married you.

116
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,720
It's just a transaction.

117
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:50,560
Your Majesty.

118
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,520
I just care about you too much,

119
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:56,490
so that is why I was jealous of the Empress.

120
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:59,400
I won't disobey you again.

121
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:03,480
Please don't be angry with me, alright?

122
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:07,640
Her Majesty the Empress has arrived.

123
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,040
Your Majesty.

124
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,520
Look at my hands.

125
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,720
I often soak them in rose water.

126
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,320
Aren't they fragrant

127
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,160
and soft?

128
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:27,200
I apologize for disturbing your leisure, Your Majesty.

129
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,200
I have come for an important matter.

130
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:31,960
What is it?

131
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:33,560
Come in.

132
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,120
Imperial Physician Wang,

133
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:42,600
please explain the cause of Ruyan's death to His Majesty.

134
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,360
Your Majesty.

135
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:45,800
The deceased, Ruyan, had foam in her mouth and nose,

136
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:48,400
and slight bleeding in her ears.

137
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:50,760
The knife wound on her chest was deep,

138
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:52,760
but there was very little bleeding.

139
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:55,520
Her cause of death was not the stab wound,

140
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:59,840
but asphyxiation caused by drowning.

